2904. FROM FRANCIS DILFT.

Hist. eccl. Supplementum p. 821. Malines. LB. App. 375. 11 February 1534.

[The letter was first published by Jo. Fecht in his Hist. ecclesiasticae sec. xvi Supplmnentum, for which see Vol. iii, p. xxiv. Of the letters to Erasmus there printed this is the only one which does not appear in the Breslau MS.

The year-date may be accepted. From Ep. 2876. 26·7 it. is clear Dilft was in Spain in May 1533, but that. in July οἱ that year he had returned to Flanders (the introd. to Ep. 1663 should be corrected accordingly). His Barcelona Oration was published at Louvain in 1533, presumably in the autumn and under his supervision.]
